  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat",
    "Thread the pork pieces onto skewers",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the olive oil, honey, apple cider vinegar, dijon mustard, salt, black pepper, and garlic powder",
    "Brush the glaze onto the pork skewers",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving",
    "Serve the skewers hot, garnished with fresh parsley"
